nodes.text: A maggot was a type of creature. The muscle maggot was native to Rattatak, while the grain maggot was a food eaten by Hutts. The screw maggot was native to Haruun Kal and gravel-maggots lived on Tatooine. The Diptera maggot was used by the Yuuzhan Vong.
Qawohl was an Abyssin Sith slave who was referred to as "Maggot."
